WEBVTT

00:00:00.000 --> 00:00:04.000
Welcome to the Institute of English Culture of Buenos Aires, ICIBA.

00:00:04.001 --> 00:00:08.000
For more than twenty years, we have been dedicated to the teaching of the English language

00:00:08.001 --> 00:00:12.000
English with commitment, quality and academic excellence.

00:00:12.001 --> 00:00:17.000
Our teaching staff is made up of highly qualified professionals.

00:00:17.001 --> 00:00:20.000
who accompany each student in their linguistic journey.

00:00:20.001 --> 00:00:24.000
from the first levels to international certifications

00:00:24.001 --> 00:00:29.000
At ICIBA, we believe that learning English is opening a door to the world.

00:00:29.001 --> 00:00:34.000
Therefore, we promote personalized teaching, with small groups.

00:00:34.001 --> 00:00:38.000
updated materials and a modern communicative approach.

00:00:38.001 --> 00:00:43.000
Whether for children, teenagers or adults, each course is designed for

00:00:43.001 --> 00:00:48.000
so that our students feel motivated, content and challenged to grow.

00:00:48.001 --> 00:00:52.000
We invite you to be part of our educational community.

00:00:52.001 --> 00:00:57.000
Because at ICIBA, we don't just teach English: WE BUILD FUTURES!.

